Name: Empress's Prayer
Desc:
[Master Level: 1] Temporarily increases ATT and MATT for 2 hours and allows you to attack higher-level monsters than usual. Remains active even when the character dies. Does not stack with Echo of Hero, and you can't receive the effects of Echo of Hero during Empress's Prayer.
Cooldown: 1 day
This skill isn't affected by Cooldown Reset and Buff Duration Bonus effects.
